ous that came with the meal. I just wish there were more of them. I would have eaten a whole plate of those, they were cooked perfectly and well flavored.\n\nOkay, so we have to talk about the sticky toffee bread pudding. Why? Well, I'm not a huge sweets person. I guess I'm getting old and crotchidy, but my wife insisted we order it, so we did, and I had a bite...then another bite, and another and another and so on. I think I ate more of it than my wife did, and I didn't want to really eat dessert at first. It was just incredible, and it is easily one of the top 3 desserts I've ever eaten. So get that and the Welly, and you're going to be a happy camper. Great to see Vegas opening some new fine dining restaurants like this. I can't wait to go back ASAP!","date":"2018-07-26 20:37:30"}
