he waiter didn't seem interested in assuring we were satisfied with our meal and it's apparent that this establishment is relying on their tourist appeal.  I'm hoping that once business slows down the quality improves.  Our experience wasn't so poor that we would never try it again, but we certainly had higher expectations out of a Ramsey-branded establishment.","date":"2018-08-19 02:42:31"}
